<isis lang="en">

    <svcsubproc>
        <title>Range Mainshaft Assembly</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Secure the output shaft in a vise with the mainshaft quill up (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13018s8">Figure 288</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13018s8" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13018s8" filename="../figg13/G13018s8.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 287. Secure Output Shaft in Vise</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">If necessary, press the bushing in the rear bore of the range mainshaft (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13018s9">Figure 289</hotlnk>) and install the mainshaft in position on the quill (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13018s9">inset, Figure 289</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13018s9" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13018s9" filename="../figg13/G13018s9.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 288. Press Bushing in Rear Bore of Range Mainshaft and Install Mainshaft in Position
                </caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the bearing in the front bore of the range mainshaft (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13018t0">Figure 290</hotlnk>). Use a small flanged-end driver to properly seat bearing
                in bore on the mainshaft quill.
            </para>
            <figure id="f13018t0" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13018t0" filename="../figg13/G13018t0.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 289. Install Bearing in Front Bore of Range Mainshaft</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install the "C" ring in the groove of the mainshaft quill to retain bearing (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f13018t1">Figure 291</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f13018t1" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g13018t1" filename="../figg13/G13018t1.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>Figure 290. Install "C" Ring in Groove of Mainshaft Quill</caption>
            </figure>
        </step1>
    </svcsubproc>
